Class QListWrapper<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.jlinq.QListWrapper<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - The type of the elements in this list.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    QList<T>, Queryable<T>, java.lang.Iterable<T>, java.util.Collection<T>, java.util.List<T>

    public class QListWrapper<T>
extends java.lang.Object
implements QList<T>
    Wraps a given list.

    Marcel Singer
